name: Type With Nothing
description:
Play it in full screen or maybe you can't see something ！！！！(Some bug ,It's my fault T T

A new hand's first LD game.

Five levels.

First level Rule:Start with the letters you can see in the keyboard, aiming to get all 26 letters. 
Once you spell a word with the letters you have and one letter you don't have, you will get that letter. 
REMEMBER, you can and must use only one at one time.
For example, you can tap 'o','n','e' and get 'e' now. You can tap "no", because you have already get them.
